<div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The primary application of this message is to transfer information related to an adverse event occurring while a patient was exposed to a product. The P07 event is an unsolicited initial individual product experience report.</p>
</div>
